ENTRY_REQUIREMENTS: The courses are open to any mature (over 21) students with an interest in developing their understanding of counselling skills and theory. You must start at Level 1. Courses are validated through NCFE, under QCA Licence.
COURSE_NAM: Counselling (Interpersonal) Skills NCFE Level 1 Award (Tuesday evening)-BU

WHO_IS_THIS_COURSE_FOR: This course will show you how to produce designs using summer flowers and foliages for special occasions using a range of containers.
